April Winchell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/April_Winchell 0 April Winchell Foley (born January 4, 1960) is an American actress, voice actress, writer, talk radio host and commentator. As of 1996, she is the official voice of Clarabelle Cow in the Disney franchise. Winchell is the daughter of Paul Winchell.
